<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Payment Failed</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .container {
      text-align: center;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      max-width: 500px;
      width: 100%;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #e74c3c;
      font-size: 2em;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    p {
      color: #555;
      font-size: 1.2em;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    a {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      font-size: 1em;
      color: #ffffff;
      background-color: #e74c3c;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }
    a:hover {
      background-color: #c0392b;
    }
  </style>
  <meta http-equiv="refresh" content="5;url=https://finafid.com/">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Payment Failed</h1>
    <p>Sorry, your payment could not be processed. Please try again later.</p>
    <p>You will be redirected to the homepage shortly.</p>
    <a href="https://finafid.com/">Go to Homepage</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
